resolution: "Fixed: visibleChangelogItems()+suggestSemverForItems(); semver from visible release sections"
expected_result: semver matches visible/emitted release sections under --limit/--since-version
actual_result: hidden-release breaking no longer leaks into bump; verified via 3 unit tests
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-05T09:50:12.655Z",codex,"Fixed: added visibleChangelogItems(options) (filter→buildSections→prune empty→limitSections→flatMap) + suggestSemverForItems(items). suggestSemver(options) now classifies visible items (identical to filterItems when no --limit/--since-version). buildChangelogDocument reuses its local visibleSections. Unit tests: breaking item in hidden v1.0.0 + feature in visible v2.0.0 → --limit 1/--since-version 2.0.0 ⇒ minor/breaking:0; no limit ⇒ major/breaking:1. 85 tests pass, default output byte-identical."
close_reason: Fixed in PR #30 (merged bf091b7)
